1>Open script runner
2>click on script editor
3>click on folder -> to create new folder
4>click on script -> to create new script file
5>write the query which you want to run and click on save
6>click on Jobs
7>create Job
8>select custom job scheduled
9>give the name
10>select the user
11>select the interval timing from the example -> when you want to run this script
12>now in inline script select the file which you have created before
13>click on add -> it will run on that time which you specified.
If you run -> it will execute the command right away.
